{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/apache/flink/compare/155885cc6d182bf0f6519a9992b21b957444b4fe...28cf30dbadabf829627781dc8aa05fbacb7ffe5a", "html_url": "https://github.com/apache/flink/compare/155885cc6d182bf0f6519a9992b21b957444b4fe...28cf30dbadabf829627781dc8aa05fbacb7ffe5a", "permalink_url": "https://github.com/apache/flink/compare/apache:155885c...apache:28cf30d", "diff_url": "https://github.com/apache/flink/compare/155885cc6d182bf0f6519a9992b21b957444b4fe...28cf30dbadabf829627781dc8aa05fbacb7ffe5a.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/apache/flink/compare/155885cc6d182bf0f6519a9992b21b957444b4fe...28cf30dbadabf829627781dc8aa05fbacb7ffe5a.patch", "base_commit": {"sha": "155885cc6d182bf0f6519a9992b21b957444b4fe", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0MjA1ODc1OTk6MTU1ODg1Y2M2ZDE4MmJmMGY2NTE5YTk5OTJiMjFiOTU3NDQ0YjRmZQ==", "commit": {"author": {"name": "Hwanju Kim", "email": "hwanjkim@amazon.com", "date": "2019-11-05T07:13:03Z"}, "committer": {"name": "Till Rohrmann", "email": "trohrmann@apache.org", "date": "2019-11-06T22:54:37Z"}, "message": "[FLINK-14589] Redundant slot requests with the same AllocationID leads to inconsistent slot table\n\nWhen a slot request is redundantly made with the same AllocationID to a\nslot index other than the already allocated one, slot table becomes\ninconsistent having two slot indices allocated but one AllocationID\nassigned to only the latest slot index. This can lead to slot leakage.\nThis patch prevents such redundent slot request from rendering\ninconsistent slot allocation state by rejecting the request.\n\nThis closes #10099.", "tree": {"sha": "1e12036bfd19772187f68509bf770b5abc400add", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/apache/flink/git/trees/1e12036bfd19772187f68509bf770b5abc400add"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/apache/flink/git/commits/155885cc6d182bf0f6519a9992b21b957444b4fe", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": true, "reason": "valid", "signature": "-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\niQIzBAABCAAdFiEEuUmfpp